{"id":5998,"date":"2021-01-04T15:20:01","date_gmt":"2021-01-04T08:20:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=5998"},"modified":"2023-06-19T10:00:41","modified_gmt":"2023-06-19T03:00:41","slug":"rem-vai-hai-lop-sang-trong-tai-quan-hoang-mai-ha-noi","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/rem-vai-hai-lop-sang-trong-tai-quan-hoang-mai-ha-noi","title":{"rendered":"R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp sang tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i qu\u1eadn Ho\u00e0ng Mai, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp sang tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i qu\u1eadn Ho\u00e0ng Mai, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><em>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i Ho\u00e0ng Mai H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a tri\u1ec7u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c Ho\u00e0ng Mai. R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng che n\u1eafng, c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng, c\u1ea3n gi\u00f3, c\u1ea3n b\u1ee5i m\u00e0 r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p tinh t\u1ebf, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, \u1ea5m c\u00fang \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m qua m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda n\u00e0y<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>1. <\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>V\u00ec sao r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i qu\u1eadn Ho\u00e0ng Mai H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m g\u1ed3m hai l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i, th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i b\u00ean tring v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 mootk s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">1.1. R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u0103ng t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cao<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u cho kh\u00f4ng gian, t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c nhau c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n v\u1edbi nhau, t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn<\/p>\n<p>Ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i, h\u1ee3p m\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng phong ph\u00fa c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u phong c\u00e1ch b\u00e0i tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau t\u1eeb sang tr\u1ecdng c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n cho t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6798\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6798\" style=\"width: 1080px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-6798 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-4.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i Ho\u00e0ng Mai t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-4.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-4-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-4-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-4-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-4-510x680.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6798\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i Ho\u00e0ng Mai t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000080; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>1.2 R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1t<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00edn cao. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec7t trong ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch linh ho\u1ea1t. Khi c\u1ea7n che ch\u1eafn \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea3 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i r\u00e8m d\u00e0y xu\u1ed1ng, gi\u00fap c\u1ea3n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o ph\u00f2n, t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian y\u00ean t\u0129nh v\u00e0 th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6799\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6799\" style=\"width: 1080px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-6799 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \" width=\"1080\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-1-1.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-1-1-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-1-1-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-1-1-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoang-mai-1-1-510x680.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6799\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><strong><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\">1.3 R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u1eafn b\u1ee5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tia UV c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi v\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y v\u00e0 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u1ee5i v\u00e0 tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm v\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng, gi\u1eef cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh<\/p>\n<p>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u00f2n gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef nhi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 tho\u00e1t nhi\u1ec7t. V\u1edbi c\u1ea3i d\u00e0y v\u00e0 l\u1edbp voan, r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u00f3 h\u1ec3 gi\u0169 nhi\u1ec7t trong ph\u00f2ng trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m chi ph\u00ed \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a gi\u1eef \u1ea5m, v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8118\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8118\" style=\"width: 1276px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8118 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/rem-vai-hai-lop-cao-cap-cho-phpng-khach-tai-au-co-3.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp b\u1ea3o b\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" width=\"1276\" height=\"956\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/rem-vai-hai-lop-cao-cap-cho-phpng-khach-tai-au-co-3.jpg 1276w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/rem-vai-hai-lop-cao-cap-cho-phpng-khach-tai-au-co-3-534x400.jpg 534w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/rem-vai-hai-lop-cao-cap-cho-phpng-khach-tai-au-co-3-1068x800.jpg 1068w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/rem-vai-hai-lop-cao-cap-cho-phpng-khach-tai-au-co-3-768x575.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/rem-vai-hai-lop-cao-cap-cho-phpng-khach-tai-au-co-3-510x382.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1276px) 100vw, 1276px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8118\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp b\u1ea3o b\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y:<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/rem-vai-hai-lop-tai-hoan-kiem-ha-noi\"><em><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i Ho\u00e0n Ki\u1ebfm, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000080; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>2. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng khi l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i Ho\u00e0ng Mai H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>So v\u1edbi r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp th\u00ec r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ho\u1eb7c g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u0103n nh\u00e0, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n sau \u0111\u00e2y:<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000080; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>2.1 L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng uy t\u00edn\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean internet ho\u1eb7c th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u00e8, ng\u01b0\u01a1i fthaan ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c<\/p>\n<p>Xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y. C\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean Website c\u1ea3u c\u00f4ng ty ho\u1eb7c tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang Web \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp<\/p>\n<p>Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y v\u00e0 h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u00e0y<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y h\u1ecfi c\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong vi\u1ec7c thi c\u00f4ng r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp v\u00e0 xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9<\/p>\n<p>Sau khi thu th\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin, h\u00e3y so s\u00e1nh c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb theo gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5. Ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8413 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/rem-cua-phong-khach-tai-giang-vo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1707\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/rem-cua-phong-khach-tai-giang-vo.jpg 1707w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/rem-cua-phong-khach-tai-giang-vo-711x400.jpg 711w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/rem-cua-phong-khach-tai-giang-vo-1400x787.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/rem-cua-phong-khach-tai-giang-vo-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/rem-cua-phong-khach-tai-giang-vo-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/rem-cua-phong-khach-tai-giang-vo-510x287.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>2.2 Ki\u1ec3m tra tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u00e0, \u00e2m tr\u1ea7n<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i Ho\u00e0ng Mai H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i khoan t\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c xem li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e2y \u0111i\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c \u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0o \u0111i qua v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1eafp khung r\u00e8m hay kh\u00f4ng? N\u1ebfu c\u00f3, h\u00e3y \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng khoan tr\u00fang g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, kh\u00e2u x\u1eed l\u00fd, kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8278 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-mau-ghi-moi-la-tai-ha-dong.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1276\" height=\"956\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-mau-ghi-moi-la-tai-ha-dong.jpg 1276w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-mau-ghi-moi-la-tai-ha-dong-534x400.jpg 534w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-mau-ghi-moi-la-tai-ha-dong-1068x800.jpg 1068w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-mau-ghi-moi-la-tai-ha-dong-768x575.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-mau-ghi-moi-la-tai-ha-dong-510x382.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1276px) 100vw, 1276px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>2.3 Kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t \u0111o \u0111\u1ea1c k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111o \u0111\u1ea1c, h\u00e3y t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eeb s\u00e0n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e9p r\u00e8m l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau th\u00ec ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. Gi\u1eefa hai l\u1edbp r\u00e8m kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u1ee5ng s\u00e1t v\u00e0o nhau v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean c\u00e1ch xa nhau qu\u00e1. C\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 khi k\u00e9o r\u00e8m s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb k\u1eb9t v\u00e0o nhau g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 m\u01b0\u1ee3t, \u0111\u1ed9 \u00eam c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111o \u0111\u1ea1c k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8271 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-tai-ha-dong-can-nang-tot.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-tai-ha-dong-can-nang-tot.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-tai-ha-dong-can-nang-tot-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-tai-ha-dong-can-nang-tot-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-tai-ha-dong-can-nang-tot-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/rem-vai-dep-tai-ha-dong-can-nang-tot-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>3. \u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 mua r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i 2 l\u1edbp \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y H\u1ed3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh 0964546888)<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao, s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cao c\u1ea5p l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Do v\u1eady, r\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng lu\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec7n nghi t\u1ea1i h\u00e0 n\u1ed9i, chuy\u00ean b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng r\u00e8m cao c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 r\u00e8m ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng nh\u01b0:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/rem-vai-hai-lop\">r<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\">\u00e8m v\u1ea3i,<\/span><\/span><\/a><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\">\u00a0<a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-go\/\">r\u00e8m g\u1ed7<\/a>,\u00a0<a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoratio